  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the toasted and ground Szechuan peppercorns and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rinsed and drained red lentils and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped walnuts and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the berbere spice and salt and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot over rice or injera bread."
